## Ubiquitous Language

## Ubiquitous Language

- common language shared through-out the business
- use same terminology
- must be precise and consistent
    - synonymous and ambiguous terms
    - glossary
    - a shared effort
- domain experts & domain knowledge
- sharing across all stakeholders
- evolves

